TheParis\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"her bout\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"a minute\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"a rival\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"a sex test\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angela Carini broke down in tears as she pulled out of the fight after just 46 seconds, having twice been caught by powerful blows from Algerian fighter Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.907036531800667, \"rank\": 0.10220823276547272, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"just 46 seconds\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"powerful blows\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was disqualified from last year's World Championships after failing a test set by the International Boxing Association (IBA), which said at the time that the 25-year-old's \\\"elevated levels of testosterone failed to meet the eligibility criteria\\\" for women's competition.\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7833338820025835e-22, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.6396568463978174, \"rank\": 0.5045216572404342, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's World Championships\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"a test\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"the 25-year-old's \\\"elevated levels\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"the eligibility criteria\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"women's competition\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has, however, been ruled eligible for the Games by the International Olympic Committee and now advances into the second round of the women's 66kg tournament.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"the second round\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 66kg tournament\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking afterwards, Carini explained she had never been hit so hard and decided to withdraw because of the intense pain in her nose.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9789157487956605, \"rank\": 0.021538371642538384, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intense pain\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"her nose\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a mature woman,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mature woman\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The ring is my life.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ring\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always been very instinctive.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And when I feel that something is not right, it's not giving up.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's having the maturity to stop.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the maturity\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's having the maturity to say: 'OK, that's enough'.\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the maturity\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Regardless of everything it's OK, fine like this.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not lose tonight \\u2026 I only did my job as a fighter.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my job\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"a fighter\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got in the ring and I fought.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not make it.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am coming out with my head held high and with a broken heart.\\\"\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"a broken heart\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was one of two boxers allowed to compete in Paris despite being disqualified from the World Championships in Delhi, with the other - Lin Yu-ting of Chinese Taipei - due to fight on Friday.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999929823389, \"rank\": 7.017740924378108e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9980204542463195, \"rank\": 0.0019800176549078937, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"en